ilding/join` | POST | `BuildingJoinRequest` | `BuildingJoinResult` | 登录时加载
建筑数据 |\n    44\t| `v1/building/build` | POST | `BuildingBuildRequest` | `Bui
ldingBuildResult` | 建造新建筑 |\n    45\t| `v1/building/remove` | POST | `Build
ingRemoveRequest` | `BuildingRemoveResult` | 拆除建筑 |\n    46\t| `v1/building/
move` | POST | `BuildingMoveRequest` | `BuildingMoveResult` | 移动建筑位置 |\n  
