ove` | 准备拆除建筑 |\n    60\t| `cityBuildingRemove` | 接收 | `CityBuildingRemo
ve` | 确认拆除建筑 |\n    61\t| `cityBuildingPreUpgrade` | 发送 | `CityBuildingP
